/****** Object:  Table [dbo].[CasualsData2024]    Script Date: 04/08/2025 09:10:01 ******/
SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON
GO
CREATE TABLE [dbo].[CasualsData2024](
	[ID] [int] IDENTITY(1,1) NOT NULL,
	[WeekNumber] [float] NULL,
	[CasualName] [nvarchar](255) NULL,
	[TimeInMonday] [nvarchar](255) NULL,
	[TimeOutMonday] [nvarchar](255) NULL,
	[MondayHours] [float] NULL,
	[MonTransport] [float] NULL,
	[MonWages] [float] NULL,
	[TimeInTuesday] [nvarchar](255) NULL,
	[TimeOutTuesday] [nvarchar](255) NULL,
	[TuesdayHours] [float] NULL,
	[TueTransport] [float] NULL,
	[TueWages] [float] NULL,
	[TimeInWednesday] [nvarchar](255) NULL,
	[TimeOutWednesday] [nvarchar](255) NULL,
	[WednesdayHours] [float] NULL,
	[WedTransport] [float] NULL,
	[WedWages] [float] NULL,
	[TimeInThursday] [nvarchar](255) NULL,
	[TimeOutThursday] [nvarchar](255) NULL,
	[ThursdayHours] [float] NULL,
	[ThursTransport] [float] NULL,
	[ThursWages] [float] NULL,
	[TimeInFriday] [nvarchar](255) NULL,
	[TimeOutFriday] [nvarchar](255) NULL,
	[FridayHours] [float] NULL,
	[FriTransport] [float] NULL,
	[FriWages] [float] NULL,
	[TimeInSaturday] [nvarchar](255) NULL,
	[TimeOutSaturday] [nvarchar](255) NULL,
	[SaturdayHours] [float] NULL,
	[SatTransport] [float] NULL,
	[SatWages] [float] NULL,
	[TimeInSunday] [nvarchar](255) NULL,
	[TimeOutSunday] [nvarchar](255) NULL,
	[SundayHours] [float] NULL,
	[SunTransport] [float] NULL,
	[SunWages] [float] NULL,
	[TotalHours]  AS (((((([MondayHours]+[TuesdayHours])+[WednesdayHours])+[ThursdayHours])+[FridayHours])+[SaturdayHours])+[SundayHours]),
	[TotalAdvances]  AS (((((([monTransport]+[TueTransport])+[WedTransport])+[ThursTransport])+[FriTransport])+[SatTransport])+[SunTransport]),
	[TotalWages]  AS (((((([monWages]+[TueWages])+[WedWages])+[ThursWages])+[FriWages])+[SatWages])+[SunWages]),
	[SSMA_TimeStamp] [timestamp] NOT NULL,
 CONSTRAINT [CasualsData2024$ID] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(
	[ID] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON, OPTIMIZE_FOR_SEQUENTIAL_KEY = OFF) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]
GO

SET ANSI_NULLS ON
GO
SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON

	[TimeOutMonday] [nvarchar](255) NULL,
	[MondayHours] [float] NULL,
	[MonTransport] [float] NULL,
	[MonWages] [float] NULL,

	[FridayHours] [float] NULL,
	[FriTransport] [float] NULL,
	[FriWages] [float] NULL,

	[TimeOutSaturday] [nvarchar](255) NULL,
	[SaturdayHours] [float] NULL,
	[SatTransport] [float] NULL,
	[SatWages] [float] NULL,
	[TimeInSunday] [nvarchar](255) NULL,
	[TimeOutSunday] [nvarchar](255) NULL,
	[SundayHours] [float] NULL,
	[SunTransport] [float] NULL,
	[SunWages] [float] NULL,
	[TotalHours]  AS (((((([MondayHours]+[TuesdayHours])+[WednesdayHours])+[ThursdayHours])+[FridayHours])+[SaturdayHours])+[SundayHours]),
	[TotalAdvances]  AS (((((([monTransport]+[TueTransport])+[WedTransport])+[ThursTransport])+[FriTransport])+[SatTransport])+[SunTransport]),

CREATE TABLE [dbo].[CasualsData2025New](
	[ID] [int] IDENTITY(1,1) NOT NULL,
	[WeekNumber] [float] NULL,
	[CasualName] [nvarchar](255) NULL,
	[TimeInMonday] [time](0) NULL,
	[TimeOutMonday] [time](0) NULL,
	[MonLunch]  AS (case when [TimeOutMonday]=[TimeInMonday] then (0) else (30) end),
	[MonTimeDeduction] [varchar](50) NULL,
	[MonHours]  AS (datediff(minute,[TimeInMonday],[TimeOutMonday])+case when [TimeOutMonday]<[TimeInMonday] then (1) else (0) end),
	[MonNotes] [ntext] NULL,
	[MonTransport] [float] NULL,
	[MonWages] [float] NULL,
	[TimeInTuesday] [time](0) NULL,
	[TimeOutTuesday] [time](0) NULL,
	[TueLunch]  AS (case when [TimeOutTuesday]=[TimeInTuesday] then (0) else (30) end),
	[TueTimeDeduction] [varchar](50) NULL,
	[TueHours]  AS (datediff(minute,[TimeInTuesday],[TimeOutTuesday])+case when [TimeOutTuesday]<[TimeInTuesday] then (1) else (0) end),
	[TueNotes] [ntext] NULL,
	[TueTransport] [float] NULL,
	[TueWages] [float] NULL,
	[TimeInWednesday] [time](0) NULL,
	[TimeOutWednesday] [time](0) NULL,
	[WedLunch]  AS (case when [TimeOutWednesday]=[TimeInWednesday] then (0) else (30) end),
	[WedTimeDeduction] [varchar](50) NULL,
	[WedHours]  AS (datediff(minute,[TimeInWednesday],[TimeOutWednesday])+case when [TimeOutWednesday]<[TimeInWednesday] then (1) else (0) end),
	[WedNotes] [ntext] NULL,
	[WedTransport] [float] NULL,
	[WedWages] [float] NULL,
	[WedNetHours]  AS (((((([MonWages]+[TueWages])+[WedWages])+[ThursWages])+[FriWages])+[SatWages])+[SunWages]),
	[TimeInThursday] [time](0) NULL,
	[TimeOutThursday] [time](0) NULL,
	[ThursLunch]  AS (case when [TimeOutThursday]=[TimeInThursday] then (0) else (30) end),
	[ThursTimeDeduction] [varchar](50) NULL,
	[ThursHours]  AS (datediff(minute,[TimeInThursday],[TimeOutThursday])+case when [TimeOutThursday]<[TimeInThursday] then (1) else (0) end),
	[ThursNotes] [ntext] NULL,
	[ThursTransport] [float] NULL,
	[ThursWages] [float] NULL,
	[TimeInFriday] [time](0) NULL,
	[TimeOutFriday] [time](0) NULL,
	[FriLunch]  AS (case when [TimeOutFriday]=[TimeInFriday] then (0) else (30) end),
	[FriTimeDeduction] [varchar](50) NULL,
	[FriHours]  AS (datediff(minute,[TimeInFriday],[TimeOutFriday])+case when [TimeOutFriday]<[TimeInFriday] then (1) else (0) end),
	[FriNotes] [ntext] NULL,
	[FriTransport] [float] NULL,
	[FriWages] [float] NULL,
	[TimeInSaturday] [time](0) NULL,
	[TimeOutSaturday] [time](0) NULL,
	[SatLunch]  AS (case when [TimeOutSaturday]=[TimeInSaturday] then (0) else (30) end),
	[SatTimeDeduction] [varchar](50) NULL,
	[SatHours]  AS (datediff(minute,[TimeInSaturday],[TimeOutSaturday])+case when [TimeOutSaturday]<[TimeInSaturday] then (1) else (0) end),
	[SatNotes] [ntext] NULL,
	[SatTransport] [float] NULL,
	[SatWages] [float] NULL,
	[TimeInSunday] [time](0) NULL,
	[TimeOutSunday] [time](0) NULL,
	[SunLunch]  AS (case when [TimeOutSunday]=[TimeInSunday] then (0) else (30) end),
	[SunTimeDeduction] [varchar](50) NULL,
	[SunHours]  AS (datediff(minute,[TimeInSunday],[TimeOutSunday])+case when [TimeOutSunday]<[TimeInSunday] then (1) else (0) end),
	[SunNotes] [ntext] NULL,
	[SunTransport] [float] NULL,
	[SunWages] [float] NULL,
	[TotalAdvances]  AS (((((([monTransport]+[TueTransport])+[WedTransport])+[ThursTransport])+[FriTransport])+[SatTransport])+[SunTransport]),
	[TotalWages]  AS (((((([MonWages]+[TueWages])+[WedWages])+[ThursWages])+[FriWages])+[SatWages])+[SunWages]),
	[TotalHours]  AS ((((((((datediff(minute,[TimeInMonday],[TimeOutMonday])+case when [TimeOutMonday]<[TimeInMonday] then (1) else (0) end)+(datediff(minute,[TimeInTuesday],[TimeOutTuesday])+case when [TimeOutTuesday]<[TimeInTuesday] then (1) else (0) end))+datediff(minute,[TimeInWednesday],[TimeOutWednesday]))+case when [TimeOutWednesday]<[TimeInWednesday] then (1) else (0) end)+(datediff(minute,[TimeInThursday],[TimeOutThursday])+case when [TimeOutThursday]<[TimeInThursday] then (1) else (0) end))+(datediff(minute,[TimeInFriday],[TimeOutFriday])+case when [TimeOutFriday]<[TimeInFriday] then (1) else (0) end))+(datediff(minute,[TimeInSaturday],[TimeOutSaturday])+case when [TimeOutSaturday]<[TimeInSaturday] then (1) else (0) end))+(datediff(minute,[TimeInSunday],[TimeOutSunday])+case when [TimeOutSunday]<[TimeInSunday] then (1) else (0) end)),
	[TotalDeductions] [varchar](50) NULL,
	[SSMA_TimeStamp] [timestamp] NOT NULL,
